signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Shutdown defenders have the talent to erase receivers from the game. When they enter the zone, their coverage is tighter and interceptions are more frequent on contested catches.

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: For great quarterbacks, vision and anticipation are paramount. When they enter the zone, their first open receiver is highlighted (while they're standing in the pocket).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws while running outside the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all unpressured throws inside the red zone (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws outside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
When playing in an indoor stadium, players with this ability can easily enter the Zone.
Defenders with this ability can still tackle effectively while trying to strip the football.
Defenders with this ability can apply pressure to the quarterback from a greater distance.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running post and corner routes.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Run Stuffers can singlehandedly disrupt an offense. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their win rate and block shed speed against one-on-one run blocks.
